                            Protocol Labs
                        </a>
                        <a 
                            aria-label="Navigate to Blueyard" 
                            target="_blank" 
                            href="https://www.blueyard.com/" 
                            class="flex bg-newneutral-100 justify-center items-center w-20 h-20 lg:w-36 lg:h-36">
